HEADWORD: Siva
<hw>Si"va</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr.
<ets>Civa</ets>, properly, kind, gracious.]</ety> <fld>(Hindoo
Myth.)</fld> <def>One of the triad of Hindoo gods. He is the avenger or
destroyer, and in modern worship symbolizes the reproductive power of
nature.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

